ou like to do?\"\n\nThat's two sentences.\n\nNow, I need to respond to the user with this greeting. But first, I should have read all required files. I have read SOUL.md, USER.md, memory files, and MEMORY.md (error, but that's fine).\n\nI think I'm ready.\n\nNow, respond.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I'm your assistant, ready to tackle whatever you have in mind. What would you like to do?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":962,"output":1044,"cacheRead":15337,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17343,"cost":{"input":0.00008658,"output":0.00030275999999999995,"cacheRead":0.000690165,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001079505}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773991303448}}
